reviews.review_text:
I am on an amazing journey I am listening to every 1994 show in order, mining for gold. 

This run is an example of '94 shows that seem to be universally derided in the comments, but actually aren't half bad when you actually listen. Not great, but not terrible. 

Set 1 Highlights: All songs played well. No major highlights though. 

Set 2 Highlights: PITB>UJB. Nice Brokedown.
